{"tid":2338172,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國已有逾100萬人接種疫苗 福西預期美國明年夏季恢復正常","createTime":"2020-12-24T00:32:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T00:57:45.000Z","uid":130626,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"635fcc1c73bf2bf6198763af90848b43b28ffb87","tid":2338172,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T00:32:28.000Z","msg":"美國國家過敏與傳染病研究所（NIAID）主管福西（Anthony Fauci）說，若接種武漢肺炎疫苗過程順利，到明年夏天，美國廣泛人口可能已獲免疫。他估計美國人明年6、7月可恢復舉辦婚禮。福西相信優先接種疫苗的群組，明年3、4月會完成接種，因此全民大規模接種會由4月開始，到夏天，估計有70-85%人口已接種疫苗，對全國構成保護傘。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201224/OWJSZCWGXRF3XOPL2IUDTCJHCI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201224%2FOWJSZCWGXRF3XOPL2IUDTCJHCI%2F&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MYZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=d675aff9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201224%2FOWJSZCWGXRF3XOPL2IUDTCJHCI%2F&h=166fb82f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201224/OWJSZCWGXRF3XOPL2IUDTCJHCI/</a>"},{"pid":"f39ea56980bbe8004604fc16f475b53b4210c54b","tid":2338172,"uid":53374,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T00:37:11.000Z","msg":"香港：限聚多一至兩年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6292735ac5b025cb1b5092d28b4e43cfb0e8abe","tid":2338172,"uid":25357,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T00:39:17.000Z","msg":"等睇變種<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff76ae6a3e87ac43d9519cc112c4d74de546e563","tid":2338172,"uid":258948,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T00:40:12.000Z","msg":"藍屍：尾國出年全部人面癱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5694c7a079588cd611b3f6259e19a49567e00860","tid":2338172,"uid":361247,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T00:43:11.000Z","msg":"都要等到明年夏季<